STATE
v.
BROWN 2019-0497 Supreme Court of Ohio. July 2, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSAL

Appellant has not filed a memorandum in support of jurisdiction, due June 28, 2019, in compliance with the Rules of Practice of the Supreme Court of Ohio and therefore has failed to prosecute this cause with the requisite diligence. Cause dismissed.
